<P>MONTALBERT A NOVEL.</P>
<P>BY CHARLOTTE SMITH.</P>
<P>IN TWO VOLUMES.</P>
<P>VOL. I.</P>
<P>PRINTED FOR MATHEW CAREY, No. 118, Market-&s;treet, Philadelphia, By GEORGE KLINE, Carli&s;le.</P>
